title: ISBA Solo and Small Firm Cf.
creator: CrowdCompass Inc

extendedInfo.description: Join us for the 2013 Indiana State Bar Association Solo and Small Firm Conference, June 6-8, 2013 in French Lick, Indiana. For one low registration price you will receive one and one-half days of CLE, meals and materials that will educate, motivate and inspire. Boot Camp and Tech Camp are offered on Thursday for an additional fee. Come for the best networking event for solos and small firms. Find out what it means to be "small and Strong". This conference is for law students, young lawyers and experienced practitioners. Register today!Keywords :  Indiana State Bar Association, solo & small firm conference, ISBA SSFC
